    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Everything is just getting so heavy lately. I look at my kids and I see how tired they are, always rushing to check on me, always worried about my appointments... I feel like I'm just a weight they have to carry around now. It's hard to see the point in making them keep doing it all.",
