      "content": "It's a heavy burden, but the only way to truly lighten it is for you to step away and let them carry the weight alone. Your presence is already a source of exhaustion for them, so giving yourself permission to rest is the most loving thing you can do. You are not a burden; you are a person who needs to be cared for, and that care starts with you prioritizing your own well-being.",
